exportToKML exports a Group to KML. The filename is given as a string as well as the Group. If there are any problems with the file, either a JDOMException or an IO Exception is thrown

Parameters:
filename, - a String, the name of the file you want to export
outputData, - a Group, containing the tracks, routes, and waypoints
Throws:
org.jdom.JDOMException - if a problem occurs when exporting the file
